sentences: Hyste'riah is a Swedish thrash metal / metallic hardcore band that originated in Landskrona in 1987.
Hyste'riah was formed by bassplayer J. B. Krown (from D.T.A.L.), drummer T. C. Hagen and guitarist Cliff T (later in Darkane and Terror 2000) at a local music festival in Landskrona.
Wild Rags, who sold about 10% of their tapes now offered them a deal for their upcoming four-song 12-inch single.
Late in 1989, Hyste'riah joined forces with the remains of Helsingborg thrashers GOD.
In 2016, the recordings from 1987 and 1988 were freshened up in Darkane studios and re-released by To The Death Records.

In 2021 new recordings were done as a solo project by founder J. B. Krown and released as Badassery CD in 2022.
